ource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr was also an assistant coach on the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s team during the 2021 during the Olympic Games in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9960945198840984, \"rank\": 0.003920783642714817, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris was the fifth consecutive gold medal for the men.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999943436251, \"rank\": 5.6564502741746346e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The other former Wildcat to bring home a gold medal was Twila Kilgore as an assistant coach on the United States women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s soccer team.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wildcat_formation\", \"score\": 0.9994521719014231, \"rank\": 0.0005470418270734109, \"text\": \"Wildcat\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wildcat_formation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wildcat_formation\"}, {\"begin\": 973, \"end\": 980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2420841180181633e-16, \"text\": \"Kilgore\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\"}, {\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_te